.  YOU KILLED THE ONLY BOT I EVER LOVED,
> THEN FRAMED ME FOR MURDER AND HIGH TREASON AGAINST THE COUNCIL OF
> ELDERS!
>

{Nightshade}

    The fem bot grinned, "I killed and framed no one maximal. My beef isn't
with you at all though in truth that's not really true, my main cause for
being reprogrammed as a preicon rather than a maximal hangs on the
de-evolution of our people. MAximals were all too ready to change and give
up their past... I wasn't and the only ones who felt the same were in the
predicons."

    Sniffing she shrugged, rubbing a hand over each of her arms feeling out
the damage done, "I fight along side some I fought years against in days
when you weren't even a flicker within the matrix. You were framed for
treason...well your entire slagging race is a treason against what I
originally fought for."

    Frowning she looked darkly at Sunhawk until the explosive force of the
energon grabbed her attention, turning her head slightly to keep an eye on
Sunhawk she glanced over her shoulder and the incomming energy wave from the
exploding alien energon... "Looks like our own fight just became moot..."
She finished before the energy rolled over their location.

    She struggled against the energy that coursed through her body dropping
her to her knees amongst the shattered earth caused by Sunhawks grenades,
her optics dimming as stasis lock shut her down...
